OL,3,CTwo men deny murder of young father
OL,5,FTwo men will face trial accused of the
OL,6,Fmurder of a 19-year-old father in Kent.
OL,8,FAt Canterbury Crown Court on Tuesday
OL,9,F(2 June), Tobias Agbaje, 21, and
OL,10,FKieron Barnes, 19, pleaded not guilty
OL,11,Fto the murder of Ashton Harrington on
OL,12,F3 April in Whitstable.
OL,14,FKent Police had been called to Belmont
OL,15,FRoad in the town just after 2am, where
OL,16,FMr Harrington was found with injuries
OL,17,Fconsistent with stab wounds and died
OL,18,Fat the scene, the force had said.
