OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780419954
OL,3,CTwo men deny murder of young father
OL,5,FAgbaje, of Claremont Street, Herne
OL,6,FBay, and Barnes, of Romney Court,
OL,7,FSittingbourne, also denied having a
OL,8,Fbladed article during the hearing.
OL,10,FKerry Waitt, defending Barnes, told
OL,11,FCanterbury Crown Court he denies any
OL,12,Finvolvement or presence at the scene.
OL,14,FJames Harrison, defending Agbaje, told
OL,15,Fthe hearing he would argue that he
OL,16,Facted in self-defence.
OL,18,FThe pair will face trial on November 3
OL,19,Fand it is expected to last three weeks.
