OL,3,CTwo men deny murder of young father
OL,5,FFollowing Mr Harrington's death, his
OL,6,Fmother Camille Harrington paid tribute
OL,7,Fto him as a doting father and said
OL,8,Fthat life would never be the same
OL,9,Fwithout him.
OL,11,FIn a statement released through Kent
OL,12,FPolice, she said: "He was the most
OL,13,Floyal, loving, funny boy with the
OL,14,Fbiggest personality and he could light
OL,15,Fup a room with his smile and laugh.
OL,17,F"He was loved by all that knew him. He
OL,18,Fwas most happy when he was with his
OL,19,Ffriends and daughter, who he
OL,20,Fabsolutely doted on.
OL,26,@tD@SOUyD@AOU
